snippet.title: Popcorned Planet
snippet.description:
A new nerd channel that will obsess over Movies, TV Shows, Video Games & other social issues that are worthy of being Honest about. But this one isn’t corporate owned or based in Hollywood. We’ll be kind and rewind, but always share whats on our mind. Welcome to Popcorned Planet.

Created by Andy Signore (Creator of ScreenJunkies, Honest Trailers, MovieFights, Man At Arms, FlickBait, Prank it FWD, Super Fan Builds, etc) and home to the Nerd Brew Crew and more.

Located in Tampa, Florida.
